<p>Location: <strong>Shanghai</strong><br />Field: <strong>Events</strong><br />Length: <strong>6 months</strong><br />Industry: <strong>Media</strong><br />Level: <strong>Intern</strong><br />Start Date: <strong>ASAP</strong></p>
