<li>Intested in Events Management</li>
<li>Attention to detail</li>
<li>Marketing Research</li>
</ul>
<p>Responsibilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>Promoting event online and offline</li>
<li>Coordinating with speakers, vendors and sponsors</li>
<li>Assisting events on behalf of the Event Director</li>
